Class ResultMessages

  • java.lang.Object
    • tools.ResultMessages

  • public class ResultMessages
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will contain and manage messages that results from any calculations performed by this package tool. Negative message number are considered errors that impeached proper calculation. Positive messages are warnings that doesn't affect the calculation result.

        public void add(java.lang.String resultMessage,
                int number)
        Add a new message to this result message container; if the message number already exists, nothing is added and the existing message will remain. Negative numbers are considered errors, while positive numbers are considered warnings.
        Parameters:
        resultMessage - The text of the message
        number - The number of the message
